description:
This is a 9 minute workout called '8 Minute 'Good Morning' Pilates Stretch | Good Moves | Well+Good' from the channel Well+Good.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 8 minute pilates workout is the perfect way to start your day! Join Chloe, from Go Chlo Pilates, for this stretch routine that will leave you feeling refreshed–you can even do it in your pajamas.

To get notified about new video uploads, subscribe to Well+Good's channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/Wellandgood

Check out more from Chloe here: https://www.youtube.com/c/GoChloPilates
